167/*
168Special symbols for undefined elements.
169 Z Symbol
170 -----------
171 113 Uut
172 114 Uuq Now Fl
173 115 Uup
174 116 Uuh Now Lv
175 117 Uus
176 118 Uuo
177*/
178
179struct PoPDatas {
180 char const *name;
181 enum PoPs_genre genre;
182 int Z, N, nuclearLevel;
183 double mass;
184};
